snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator 2 | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing PowerWash Simulator 2!

https://bit.ly/PWS2Steam

It's time to return to the grime & continue where you left off in Muckingham to fight back that filth with a whole new career to work through.

Coming 2025 to Steam, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5 and Epic Games Store

Wishlist PowerWash Simulator 2 here:
https://bit.ly/PWS2Steam
https://bit.ly/PWS2Epic
Follow our socials here: https://bit.ly/PWSSocial
Join our Discord: https://www.discord.gg/powerwashsimulator
